false, and Musk is appealing that ruling. As part of that appeal, a lot mor=
e details have been made public about Musk=E2=80=99s 2018 conversations wit=
h the Saudi PIF and, uh, yeah, you can see why the judge ruled that the fun=
ding was not secure? From  Bloomberg News:Now, a series of text messages th=
at Musk exchanged with Silicon Valley friends, investors and the managing d=
